name: 双手叉腰 / arms akimbo  (full body)
description:
再正常不过的双手叉腰姿势了,我只是把他用controlnet固定了下来

Just a normal hand-on-hips pose, I just stabilized it with ControlNet

推荐的tag为:standing,hands on hips,full body.除此之外也可以加上from above之类的或者bent over之类的tag

The recommended tags are: standing, hands on hips, full body. Besides these, you can also add tags like "from above" or "bent over" if applicable.

附赠了摆姿势用的恋活人物的深度图,有兴趣可以试试

There is a depth map included in the file, which is the depth map of the poseable Koikatu character I used. If you're interested, you can try it out.

请使用controlnet识别运行这个动作

推荐预处理器选择"无"，模型使用为"openpose-fp16"

Please use ControlNet to recognize and execute this action.

It is recommended to select "none" as the preprocessor, and "openpose-fp16" as the model to use.
